---
// AeonCircle — The Healthspan Club
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
<title>AeonCircle — Live well, for 120 years.</title>
<meta name="description" content="A membership built for your healthspan. The wealthy have private health teams — AeonCircle gives one to everyone else. Curated regimens, personalized plans, and life insurance aligned with the next 120 years of your life." />
<link rel="canonical" href="https://aeoncircle.com/" />
<meta property="og:type" content="website" />
<meta property="og:url" content="https://aeoncircle.com/" />
<meta property="og:title" content="AeonCircle — Live well, for 120 years." />
<meta property="og:description" content="The healthspan club. One membership. Curated regimens, personalized plans, life insurance aligned with your next 120 years. We do the thinking. You live well." />
<meta property="og:site_name" content="AeonCircle" />
<meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
<meta name="twitter:title" content="AeonCircle — Live well, for 120 years." />
<meta name="twitter:description" content="The healthspan club. One membership. We do the thinking. You live well." />
<meta name="theme-color" content="#FBF7EE" />
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:ital,opsz,wght,SOFT,WONK@0,9..144,300..900,0..100,0..1;1,9..144,300..900,0..100,0..1&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #FBF7EE;
    --bg-2: #F3E8D5;
    --fg: #1F3D32;
    --fg-2: #355745;
    --muted: #7A8B7F;
    --accent: #D17B47;
    --accent-2: #5C8973;
    --accent-3: #E89C68;
    --line: rgba(31, 61, 50, 0.12);
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  html, body { margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--fg);
    font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    overflow-x: hidden;
    min-height: 100vh;
    position: relative;
  }
  .bg {
    position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 0; overflow: hidden;
    background:
      radial-gradient(1000px 700px at 50% 110%, rgba(92,137,115,0.20), transparent 65%),
      radial-gradient(800px 500px at 80% -5%, rgba(209,123,71,0.12), transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(600px 500px at 15% 30%, rgba(232,156,104,0.08), transparent 65%),
      var(--bg);
  }
  .bg::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute; inset: -2px;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='160' height='160'><filter id='n'><feTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.85' numOctaves='2' stitchTiles='stitch'/><feColorMatrix values='0 0 0 0 0.12  0 0 0 0 0.24  0 0 0 0 0.20  0 0 0 0.06 0'/></filter><rect width='100%' height='100%' filter='url(%23n)'/></svg>");
    opacity: 0.7;
    pointer-events: none;
    mix-blend-mode: multiply;
  }
  .halo {
    position: absolute; left: 50%; top: 50%;
    width: min(70vmin, 620px); aspect-ratio: 1/1;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    background: radial-gradient(circle,
      rgba(209,123,71,0.22) 0%,
      rgba(232,156,104,0.10) 35%,
      rgba(92,137,115,0.05) 60%,
      transparent 75%);
    border-radius: 50%;
    filter: blur(30px);
    animation: breathe 9s ease-in-out infinite;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  @keyframes breathe {
    0%, 100% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1); opacity: 0.85; }
    50%      { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1.10); opacity: 1; }
  }
  .rings {
    position: absolute; left: 50%; top: 50%;
    width: min(85vmin, 780px); aspect-ratio: 1/1;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    z-index: 1;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .ring {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    border: 1px solid rgba(31, 61, 50, 0.14);
    border-radius: 50%;
    animation: spin 80s linear infinite;
  }
  .ring.r2 { inset: 8%;  border-color: rgba(92,137,115,0.22); animation-duration: 110s; animation-direction: reverse; }
  .ring.r3 { inset: 18%; border: 1px dashed rgba(209,123,71,0.18); animation-duration: 140s; }
  .ring.r4 { inset: 28%; border-color: rgba(31,61,50,0.08); animation-duration: 170s; animation-direction: reverse; }
  .ring .dot {
    position: absolute; left: 50%; top: -4px;
    width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent);
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    box-shadow: 0 0 16px rgba(209,123,71,0.6);
  }
  .ring.r2 .dot { background: var(--accent-2); box-shadow: 0 0 16px rgba(92,137,115,0.6); }
  @keyframes spin { from { transform: rotate(0); } to { transform: rotate(360deg); } }

  .wrap { position: relative; z-index: 2; min-height: 100vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
  header {
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    padding: 28px 40px;
  }
  .brand {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-weight: 500; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0;
    color: var(--fg);
  }
  .brand-mark {
    width: 22px; height: 22px; border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--accent);
    position: relative;
  }
  .brand-mark::before {
    content: ""; position: absolute; inset: 4px;
    border-radius: 50%; background: var(--accent);
  }
  .nav-meta {
    color: var(--fg-2);
    font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase; opacity: 0.8;
  }
  main {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px 24px 80px;
  }
  .eyebrow {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
    padding: 7px 16px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
    border-radius: 999px;
    color: var(--fg-2);
    font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.24em; text-transform: uppercase;
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
  }
  .eyebrow .pulse {
    width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(209,123,71,0.55);
    animation: pulse 2.2s ease-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes pulse {
    0%   { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0   rgba(209,123,71,0.55); }
    100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 14px rgba(209,123,71,0); }
  }
  h1 {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', 'Noto Serif SC', serif;
    font-size: clamp(64px, 12.5vw, 184px);
    line-height: 0.92;
    margin: 30px 0 6px;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-variation-settings: "opsz" 144, "SOFT" 100, "WONK" 0;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    color: var(--fg);
  }
  h1 .accent {
    font-style: italic;
    font-variation-settings: "opsz" 144, "SOFT" 100, "WONK" 1;
    background: linear-gradient(120deg, var(--accent) 0%, var(--accent-3) 50%, var(--accent) 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    color: transparent;
  }
  .lead {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-size: clamp(22px, 2.8vw, 34px);
    color: var(--fg);
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin: 14px 0 32px;
    line-height: 1.25;
    font-variation-settings: "opsz" 72, "SOFT" 50;
  }
  .lead em {
    font-style: italic; font-weight: 500;
    background: linear-gradient(120deg, var(--accent) 0%, var(--accent-3) 50%, var(--accent) 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    color: transparent;
  }
  .pitch {
    font-size: clamp(15px, 1.4vw, 17px);
    color: var(--fg-2);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 40px;
    line-height: 1.78;
  }
  .pitch strong { color: var(--fg); font-weight: 500; }
  .cta-row { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
  .cta {
    background: var(--fg);
    color: var(--bg);
    border: 0;
    padding: 15px 28px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer;
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
    transition: transform .25s ease, background .25s ease, box-shadow .25s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 22px rgba(31,61,50,0.18);
  }
  .cta .arrow { display: inline-block; transition: transform .25s ease; }
  .cta:hover {
    background: var(--accent);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 28px rgba(209,123,71,0.25);
  }
  .cta:hover .arrow { transform: translateX(4px); }
  .cta-note { color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.08em; }
  .meta-row {
    margin-top: 60px;
    display: flex; gap: 26px;
    color: var(--fg-2);
    font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.24em; text-transform: uppercase;
    flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }
  .meta-row span { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
  .meta-row span::before {
    content: ""; width: 4px; height: 4px;
    background: var(--accent); border-radius: 50%;
  }
  footer {
    padding: 28px 40px;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  footer a { color: var(--fg-2); text-decoration: none; transition: color .2s; }
  footer a:hover { color: var(--accent); }
  .fade { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(14px); animation: fade .9s ease forwards; }
  .fade.d1 { animation-delay: .15s; }
  .fade.d2 { animation-delay: .35s; }
  .fade.d3 { animation-delay: .55s; }
  .fade.d4 { animation-delay: .75s; }
  .fade.d5 { animation-delay: .95s; }
  .fade.d6 { animation-delay: 1.15s; }
  @keyframes fade { to { opacity: 1; transform: none; } }
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    header, footer { padding: 20px; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; align-items: flex-start; }
    footer { align-items: center; flex-direction: row; }
    .meta-row { gap: 18px; margin-top: 44px; }
    .pitch { font-size: 14.5px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="bg"></div>
  <div class="halo" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="rings" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="ring r1"><span class="dot"></span></div>
    <div class="ring r2"><span class="dot"></span></div>
    <div class="ring r3"></div>
    <div class="ring r4"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="wrap">
    <header class="fade">
      <div class="brand">
        <span class="brand-mark"></span>
        <span>AeonCircle</span>
      </div>
      <div class="nav-meta">The Healthspan Club · Now Forming</div>
    </header>

    <main>
      <div class="eyebrow fade d1">
        <span class="pulse"></span>
        <span>Membership · Now forming</span>
      </div>

      <h1 class="fade d2">
        Aeon<span class="accent">Circle</span>
      </h1>

      <p class="lead fade d3">
        Live well — for <em>120 years</em>.
      </p>

      <p class="pitch fade d4">
        The wealthy have private health teams.
        <strong>AeonCircle gives one to everyone else</strong> —
        a single membership of curated regimens, personalized plans,
        and life insurance aligned with your healthspan.
        <br/><br/>
        You live well. We do the thinking.
      </p>

      <div class="cta-row fade d5">
        <a class="cta" href="mailto:dayong.zhang@gmail.com?subject=AeonCircle%20%E2%80%94%20Invitation%20request&amp;body=Hi%20%E2%80%94%20I%27d%20like%20to%20join%20the%20founding%20circle.%0A%0AA%20little%20about%20me%3A%0A">
          <span class="label">Request invitation</span>
          <span class="arrow">→</span>
        </a>
        <span class="cta-note">Founding membership opens soon</span>
      </div>

      <div class="meta-row fade d6">
        <span>Membership</span>
        <span>Vetted</span>
        <span>Covered</span>
        <span>120 Years</span>
      </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="fade d6">
      <div>© 2026 <a href="https://aeoncircle.com/">aeoncircle.com</a></div>
      <div><a href="mailto:dayong.zhang@gmail.com">Get in touch →</a></div>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
